  "body": "<div id=\"post-view220042752294\" class=\"post-view pcol2 _param(1) _postViewArea220042752294\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div style=\"font-size:10pt; font-family:'957317_10';\" class=\"view\"><p><font face=\"굴림\" size=\"3\">\r\n\r\n</font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt;\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><font face=\"맑은 고딕\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">자궁근종</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">\r\n(Uterine Leiomyoma)<!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --></span></font></b></p><p><font face=\"굴림\" size=\"3\">\r\n\r\n</font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt;\"><font face=\"맑은 고딕\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">정의 </span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">: </span><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">자궁의 평활근세포가 국소적으로 증식한 것</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --></span></font></p><p><font face=\"굴림\" size=\"3\">\r\n\r\n</font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt;\"><font face=\"맑은 고딕\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">발생시기 </span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">: </span><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">가임기 여성에서 나타나며 <u>폐경 이후에는 퇴행한다</u></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">.<!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --></span></font></p><p><font face=\"굴림\" size=\"3\">\r\n\r\n</font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt;\"><font face=\"맑은 고딕\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">치료 </span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">: </span><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">무증상</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">(</span><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">근종환자의\r\n</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">50~60%)</span><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">인 경우 치료가 필요 없다</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">. </span><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">심하거나 불규칙한\r\n출혈 혹은 불임 등을 초래할 때는 치료가 필요</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">. </span><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">크기가 커져 골반의 통증</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">, </span><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">압박감</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">, </span><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">빈뇨 및 변비 등의 증상을 유발하면 치료 고려</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">.<!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --></span></font></p><p><font face=\"굴림\" size=\"3\">\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140627_271/isuhani_1403829495217Fsa1u_JPEG/images_%2811%29.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"259\" height=\"194\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 194px; rwidth: 259px;\" id=\"20140627_271/isuhani_1403829495217Fsa1u_JPEG/images_%2811%29.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000333B91F126')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140627_271/isuhani_1403829495217Fsa1u_JPEG/images_%2811%29.jpg?type=w3\"></span></font></p><p><font face=\"굴림\" size=\"3\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">&#8203;</span></font></p><p><font face=\"굴림\" size=\"3\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">&#8203;</span></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt;\"><font face=\"맑은 고딕\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">원인 </span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">: </span><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">불명</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --></span></font></p><p><font face=\"굴림\" size=\"3\">\r\n\r\n</font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt;\"><font face=\"맑은 고딕\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">특징 </span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">: Estrogen</span><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">에 반응</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">.\r\n<u>Estrogen </u></span><u><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">이 증가하면 크기 증가</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">, </span><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">줄어들면 성장 멈추거나 위축</span></u><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">.<!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --></span></font></p><p><font face=\"굴림\" size=\"3\">\r\n\r\n</font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt;\"><font face=\"맑은 고딕\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">분류</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --></span></font></p><p><font face=\"굴림\" size=\"3\">\r\n\r\n</font></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt 38pt; text-indent: -18pt; mso-para-margin-left: 0gd; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!--[if !supportLists]><span lang=\"EN-US\" style='mso-fareast-font-family: \"맑은 고딕\"; mso-ascii-font-family: \"맑은 고딕\"; mso-hansi-font-family: \"맑은 고딕\"; mso-bidi-font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\"><font face=\"맑은 고딕\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">-</span></font><span style=\"font: 7pt/normal 굴림, gulim; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span></span><![endif]--><font face=\"맑은 고딕\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">점막하 </span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">&#8211; </span><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">다량의 지속적인 출혈</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">.<!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --></span></font></p><p><font face=\"굴림\" size=\"3\">\r\n\r\n</font></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt 38pt; text-indent: -18pt; mso-para-margin-left: 0gd; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!--[if !supportLists]><span lang=\"EN-US\" style='mso-fareast-font-family: \"맑은 고딕\"; mso-ascii-font-family: \"맑은 고딕\"; mso-hansi-font-family: \"맑은 고딕\"; mso-bidi-font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\"><font face=\"맑은 고딕\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">-</span></font><span style=\"font: 7pt/normal 굴림, gulim; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span></span><![endif]--><font face=\"맑은 고딕\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">근층내 </span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">&#8211; </span><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">가장 흔함</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">.<!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --></span></font></p><p><font face=\"굴림\" size=\"3\">\r\n\r\n</font></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt 38pt; text-indent: -18pt; mso-para-margin-left: 0gd; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!--[if !supportLists]><span lang=\"EN-US\" style='mso-fareast-font-family: \"맑은 고딕\"; mso-ascii-font-family: \"맑은 고딕\"; mso-hansi-font-family: \"맑은 고딕\"; mso-bidi-font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\"><font face=\"맑은 고딕\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">-</span></font><span style=\"font: 7pt/normal 굴림, gulim; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span></span><![endif]--><font face=\"맑은 고딕\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">장막하</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --></span></font></p><p><font face=\"굴림\" size=\"3\">\r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140627_218/isuhani_1403829495377sbAgw_JPEG/%B4%D9%BF%EE%B7%CE%B5%E5_%287%29.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"229\" height=\"219\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 219px; rwidth: 229px;\" id=\"20140627_218/isuhani_1403829495377sbAgw_JPEG/%B4%D9%BF%EE%B7%CE%B5%E5_%287%29.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000333B91F126')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140627_218/isuhani_1403829495377sbAgw_JPEG/%B4%D9%BF%EE%B7%CE%B5%E5_%287%29.jpg?type=w3\"></font></p><p><font face=\"굴림\" size=\"3\"></font>&nbsp;</p><p><font face=\"굴림\" size=\"3\"></font>&nbsp;</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt;\"><font face=\"맑은 고딕\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">자궁선근증과 감별 필요 </span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">&#8211; </span><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">가성 피막이 근종주변에 한정 </span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">vs </span><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">가성 피박이 자궁 근층 전체에 분포</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --></span></font></p><p><font face=\"굴림\" size=\"3\">\r\n\r\n</font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt;\"><font face=\"맑은 고딕\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">악성화 여부는 명확치 않으나 거의 없다고 본다</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">.<!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --></span></font></p><p><font face=\"굴림\" size=\"3\">\r\n\r\n</font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt;\"><font face=\"맑은 고딕\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">위험인자 </span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">: </span><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">흑인</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">, </span><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">비흡연자</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">, </span><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">비만여성</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">. <!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --></span></font></p><p><font face=\"굴림\" size=\"3\">\r\n\r\n</font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt;\"><font face=\"맑은 고딕\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">증상</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --></span></font></p><p><font face=\"굴림\" size=\"3\">\r\n\r\n</font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt;\"><font face=\"맑은 고딕\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">출혈 </span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">&#8211; </span><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">기간이 길고 다량의 출혈</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">(</span><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">월경과다</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\"> - </span><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">빈혈유발</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">), </span><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">자궁내막의 궤양</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --></span></font></p><p><font face=\"굴림\" size=\"3\">\r\n\r\n</font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt;\"><font face=\"맑은 고딕\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">압박증상 </span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">&#8211; </span><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">골반의 압박감과 복부 팽만</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">, </span><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">변비와 직장의 압박감</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">, </span><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">빈뇨 및 소변 저류</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --></span></font></p><p><font face=\"굴림\" size=\"3\">\r\n\r\n</font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt;\"><font face=\"맑은 고딕\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">통증 </span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">&#8211; </span><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">속발월경통</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">, </span><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">급성경색</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">(</span><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">특히 임신시</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">), </span><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">성교통</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --></span></font></p><p><font face=\"굴림\" size=\"3\">\r\n\r\n</font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt;\"><font face=\"맑은 고딕\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">임신의 어려움 </span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">&#8211; </span><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">불임</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">(2~10%.\r\n</span><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">착상 실패 혹은 자연 유산</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">), </span><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">태아 위치이상</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">, </span><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">자궁내\r\n성장 제한</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">, </span><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">조기진통 및 분만</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">, </span><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">제왕절개분만 증가</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --></span></font></p><p><font face=\"굴림\" size=\"3\">\r\n\r\n</font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt;\"><font face=\"맑은 고딕\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">진단 </span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">: </span><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">골반 초음파 검사</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">. </span><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">자궁강\r\n내의 폴립과 점막하 근종을 감별하는데에는 자궁난관조영술</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">(HSG)</span><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">이나 생리식염주 주입 초음파 자궁조영</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">. </span><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">자궁선근증과의 감별에는 </span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">MRI<!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --></span></font></p><p><font face=\"굴림\" size=\"3\">\r\n\r\n</font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt;\"><font face=\"맑은 고딕\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">진단은 확실해야 하며 <u>반드시 다른 골반 종양을 배제해야</u> 하고</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">, </span><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">급속하게\r\n자라는 근종은 </span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">6</span><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">개월마다 </span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">follow up.<!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --></span></font></p><p><font face=\"굴림\" size=\"3\">\r\n\r\n</font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt;\"><font face=\"맑은 고딕\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">치료</span></font></p><p><font face=\"굴림\" size=\"3\">\r\n\r\n</font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt;\"><font face=\"맑은 고딕\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">내과적 치료</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\"> medroxyprogesterone(Provera),\r\ndanazol </span><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">및 성선자극호르몬 유리호르몬</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">(gonadotropin-realeasing\r\nhormone, GnRH) </span><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">작용제</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">(nafarelin acetate, Depot Lupron)</span><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">가\r\n순환 </span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">estrogen</span><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">치를 감소시켜 근종을 수축시킬 수 있지만 <u>치료 중단시 다시 커진다</u></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">. <!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --></span></font></p><p><font face=\"굴림\" size=\"3\">\r\n\r\n</font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt;\"><font face=\"맑은 고딕\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">자궁동맥색전출</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">(uterine artery embolization; UAE)</span><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">도\r\n증상이 있는 자궁근종의 덜 침습적인 치료로 많이 이용</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">.<!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --></span></font></p><p><font face=\"굴림\" size=\"3\">\r\n\r\n<br style=\"clear: both;\" /><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140627_54/isuhani_1403829669679jCzqv_JPEG/uterine_artery_embolization.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"246\" height=\"205\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 205px; rwidth: 246px;\" id=\"20140627_54/isuhani_1403829669679jCzqv_JPEG/uterine_artery_embolization.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000333B91F126')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140627_54/isuhani_1403829669679jCzqv_JPEG/uterine_artery_embolization.jpg?type=w3\"></font></p><p><font face=\"굴림\" size=\"3\"></font>&nbsp;</p><p><font face=\"굴림\" size=\"3\"></font>&nbsp;</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt;\"><font face=\"맑은 고딕\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">근종절제술</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">(myomectomy)</span><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">은 자궁벽에서 하나 혹은 그 이상의\r\n자궁근종을 절제하는 것으로 증상이 있으면서 출산 능력을 유지하기를 바라는 여성에서 시행하며 자궁경이나 복강경을 통해서</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">, </span><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">혹은 복식으로 시행할 수 있다</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">. <u>50%</u></span><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\"><u>에서 다시 근종이 생기며 통증이나\r\n불임등의 합병증 가능</u></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">.</span></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt;\"><font face=\"맑은 고딕\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">&#8203;</span></font></p><p><font face=\"굴림\" size=\"3\">\r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140627_122/isuhani_1403829669475qC5q2_JPEG/myomectomy.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"254\" height=\"198\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 198px; rwidth: 254px;\" id=\"20140627_122/isuhani_1403829669475qC5q2_JPEG/myomectomy.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000333B91F126')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140627_122/isuhani_1403829669475qC5q2_JPEG/myomectomy.jpg?type=w3\"></font></p><p><font face=\"굴림\" size=\"3\"></font>&nbsp;</p><p><font face=\"굴림\" size=\"3\"></font>&nbsp;</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt;\"><font face=\"맑은 고딕\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\"><u>자궁근종의 근본적인 치료는 자궁절제술이다</u></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\"><u>.</u> </span><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">작은 자궁근종은 질식 자궁절제술로</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">, </span><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">크거나 수가 많을 때는 복식 자궁절제술을 시행한다</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">. 45</span><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">세 이하의\r\n여성이 난소의 모양이 정상이면 난소를 보존</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">.<!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --></span></font></p><p><font face=\"굴림\" size=\"3\">\r\n\r\n</font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt;\"><font face=\"맑은 고딕\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">자궁근종 수술 처치의 적응증 </span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">: </span></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt;\"><font face=\"맑은 고딕\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">1.</span><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">빈혈을 초래할 정도의 이상 자궁출혈</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">, </span></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt;\"><font face=\"맑은 고딕\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">2.</span><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">심한 골반 통증 혹은 속발무월경</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">, </span></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt;\"><font face=\"맑은 고딕\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">3.</span><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">임신 </span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">12</span><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">주 이상의 크기로 부속기 진찰이 분명하지 않을 때</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">, </span></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt;\"><font face=\"맑은 고딕\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">4.</span><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">빈뇨</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">, </span><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">소변 정체 혹은 수신증</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">, </span></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt;\"><font face=\"맑은 고딕\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">5.</span><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">폐경 후에 커질 때</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">,</span></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt;\"><font face=\"맑은 고딕\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">6.</span><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">반복되는 유산 혹은 불임</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">, </span></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt;\"><font face=\"맑은 고딕\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">7.</span><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">크기가 급속하게 커질 때</span></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt;\"><font face=\"맑은 고딕\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">&#8203;</span></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt;\"><font face=\"맑은 고딕\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">&#8203;--------------------------------</span></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt;\"><font face=\"맑은 고딕\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">자궁근종은 호르몬제 등 양약을 복용하여 치료하기도 하지만, 부작용이 우려되고 치료를 중단하면 다시 크기가 커지게 된다. </span></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt;\"><font face=\"맑은 고딕\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">근종이 있는 부위만 제거하는 근종절제술도 시행이 되지만 수술을 받은 환자의 절반은 다시 재발하게 된다. </span></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt;\"><font face=\"맑은 고딕\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">오직 자궁절제술, 즉 자궁을 통째로 적출하는 수술만이 자궁근종을 완치시키는 방법인데, 자궁적출 후 발생하는 부작용이 만만치 않다. </span></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt;\"><font face=\"맑은 고딕\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">&#8203;</span></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt;\"><font face=\"맑은 고딕\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">출혈, 통증, 불임 등의 자궁근종으로 인한 증상이 없다면 6개월~1년 간격으로 크기가 커지지 않는지만 확인하면서 별다른 치료 없이 생활하면 되겠다. &#8203;</span></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt;\"><font face=\"맑은 고딕\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">&#8203;증상이 있는데 크기가 크지 않다면 침, 뜸, 한약 등의 한방치료로 증상을 치료한 후 역시나 크기가 커지지 않는지 경과를 관찰하면 되겠다. </span></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt;\"><font face=\"맑은 고딕\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">&#8203;</span></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt;\"><font face=\"맑은 고딕\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">증상은 없는데 크기가 너무 큰 경우에는 자궁적출수술을 시행하기 전에 한약처방으로 자궁근종의 크기를 줄이기 위한 시도를 해볼 필요가 있다. 폐경이후에는 자연적으로 크기가 작아지기 때문에 폐경전까지만 잘 관리되면 되겠다. </span></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt;\"><font face=\"맑은 고딕\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">증상도&nbsp;심하고 크기도 크다면&#8203; 수술을 우선 고려해야겠지만, 역시나 1개월~3개월 정도의 한방치료를 통해 수술없이 치료하고 관리할 수 있는 가능성을 확인해보는 것도 좋겠다. </span></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt;\"><font face=\"맑은 고딕\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">자궁을 유지하는 것과, 자궁을 적출하는 것은 여성에게는 굉장히 커다란 차이가 있기 때문.</span></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt;\"><font face=\"맑은 고딕\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">&#8203;</span></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt;\"><font face=\"맑은 고딕\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\"><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140627_247/isuhani_1403829905857hR6sm_JPEG/%B4%D9%BF%EE%B7%CE%B5%E5_%281%29_EMa.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"183\" height=\"275\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 275px; rwidth: 183px;\" id=\"20140627_247/isuhani_1403829905857hR6sm_JPEG/%B4%D9%BF%EE%B7%CE%B5%E5_%281%29_EMa.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000333B91F126')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140627_247/isuhani_1403829905857hR6sm_JPEG/%B4%D9%BF%EE%B7%CE%B5%E5_%281%29_EMa.jpg?type=w3\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140627_274/isuhani_1403829906116al6Vo_JPEG/imagesCAIST8T8.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"214\" height=\"214\" style=\"cursor: pointer;border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); rheight: 214px; rwidth: 214px;\" id=\"20140627_274/isuhani_1403829906116al6Vo_JPEG/imagesCAIST8T8.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000333B91F126')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140627_274/isuhani_1403829906116al6Vo_JPEG/imagesCAIST8T8.jpg?type=w3\"></span><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140627_136/isuhani_1403829906048E3DCu_JPEG/%B4%D9%BF%EE%B7%CE%B5%E5_%281%29_%C4%A7.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"361\" height=\"140\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 140px; rwidth: 361px;\" id=\"20140627_136/isuhani_1403829906048E3DCu_JPEG/%B4%D9%BF%EE%B7%CE%B5%E5_%281%29_%C4%A7.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000333B91F126')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140627_136/isuhani_1403829906048E3DCu_JPEG/%B4%D9%BF%EE%B7%CE%B5%E5_%281%29_%C4%A7.jpg?type=w3\"><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><br style=\"clear: both;\" />&#8203;</span></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt;\"><font face=\"맑은 고딕\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim; font-size: 11pt;\">한약치료로 자궁근종의 크기를 줄이고 &#8203;다양한 부수증상을 효과적으로 치료했다는 다수의 임상사례와 연구논문들이 있으니 자궁근종의 치료를 원하는 여성분은 한방치료를 받아보는걸 추천한다.</span></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt;\"><font face=\"맑은 고딕\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">&#8203;</span></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt;\"><font face=\"맑은 고딕\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140627_280/isuhani_1403829955130mPKLh_PNG/C7D11.PNG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"547\" height=\"172\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 172px; rwidth: 547px;\" id=\"20140627_280/isuhani_1403829955130mPKLh_PNG/C7D11.PNG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000333B91F126')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140627_280/isuhani_1403829955130mPKLh_PNG/C7D11.PNG?type=w3\"></span></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt;\"><font face=\"맑은 고딕\"><span style=\"font-family: 굴림,gulim;\">&#8203;<img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140627_85/isuhani_1403829974983bHazl_JPEG/%B0%E6%C8%F1%C0%CC%BC%F6%C7%D1%C0%C7%BF%F8Logo-%C0%A5%BF%EB_%BB%E7%C0%CC%C1%EE_%C3%E0%BC%D2.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"193\" height=\"48\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 48px; rwidth: 193px;\" id=\"20140627_85/isuhani_1403829974983bHazl_JPEG/%B0%E6%C8%F1%C0%CC%BC%F6%C7%D1%C0%C7%BF%F8Logo-%C0%A5%BF%EB_%BB%E7%C0%CC%C1%EE_%C3%E0%BC%D2.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000333B91F126')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140627_85/isuhani_1403829974983bHazl_JPEG/%B0%E6%C8%F1%C0%CC%BC%F6%C7%D1%C0%C7%BF%F8Logo-%C0%A5%BF%EB_%BB%E7%C0%CC%C1%EE_%C3%E0%BC%D2.jpg?type=w3\"></span></font></p></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>",
